text: :sun_with_face:Good morning Superpathers! Great to meet y'all! I'm a freelance B2B SaaS and healthcare content writer and strategist. I operate my own agency, <https://hardkorecontent.com/|Hard Kore Content Marketing>, here on the East Coast of Florida. Specialties include DTC & ecommerce. I've worked with awesome startups and some of the world's largest SaaS companies. From email nurtures and social ads to eBooks, white papers and blog posts, I bring creativity and inspiration to everything I do. Looking forward to connecting with everyone here.
